description._content: Repository: California Historical Society Digital object ID: Kemble Spec Col 09_B196 Call Number: Kemble Spec Col 09 Collection: California Lettersheet Collection Date: 1858 March 20 Physical Description: Wood engraving; 20 x 25 cm. overall.
